                      <span>2004-06-24</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Cederholm's book is a definite read. The language is straight-forward & constructive & the overall layout of the book is intuitive. The book is filled with everything from practical to advance tips for pushing design and functionality. At a time when more and more programming whizes are putting their skills into words, you wish all could be as effective and solution-oriented. Put simply (the author's mantra), the book is a buy. You won't be disappointed.</span>
                  
              
